id: pm-qnl2
title: "Wave 1 active graph enrichment: connect strategic stories, decisions, delivery slices, evidence, and execution order from reviewed findings"
description: "Apply only high-confidence, evidence-backed relationship changes to active items and verify each bounded batch before continuing."
type: Task
status: open
priority: 2
tags[6]: active-items,backfill,graph,relationships,task,"wave:1"
created_at: "2026-07-13T22:00:05.456Z"
updated_at: "2026-07-13T22:00:05.456Z"
author: codex-root
estimated_minutes: 720
acceptance_criteria: "Consume only reviewed Wave 0 findings and accepted edge semantics; every operation includes source evidence, confidence, author, and rationale; Prioritize story-to-delivery, decision-to-implementation, prerequisite ordering, discovered-from, evidence, release, incident, and SDK-to-adapter relationships; Partition work by canonical lineage and bounded item count so agents can claim non-overlapping batches and resume from durable cursors; Each batch runs duplicate, semantic graph, lifecycle, history-drift, and health validation and records graph-quality and token-context deltas; Low-confidence and conflicting cases remain investigations or waivers; no generic related edge is added solely for connectivity; Finish when every active item has a reviewed classification and either valid relationships, an intentional-isolate waiver, or an explicit remediation owner"
goal: project management = context management
objective: Make active execution and strategy lineages richly traversable without adding arbitrary density
value: "Agents gain reliable prerequisite, delivery, decision, evidence, and impact paths for current work first"
impact: "Improves claim-next, planning, context assembly, duplicate prevention, handoffs, and blast-radius reasoning"
outcome: "Reviewed active-item relationship batches with before and after metrics, immutable evidence, and no unexplained policy violations"
why_now: "Active work has the highest context value and lowest changelog risk, while several bodies already provide direct evidence for missing prerequisites"
parent: pm-a8zm
risk: medium
confidence: medium
