comments[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-13T22:00:05.456Z",codex-root,"Duplicate check 2026-07-13: no existing open item owns systematic evidence-backed active-item relationship enrichment across capability lineages; existing epics own their features while this task owns only cross-lineage graph remediation batches."
body: "## Priority order\n\n1. Priority-zero and priority-one stories and decisions.\n2. SDK-first and CLI simplification delivery chains.\n3. Context engine, scale, history integrity, releases, packages, and governance.\n4. Remaining active features, tasks, chores, plans, issues, and reminders.\n\n## Batch contract\n\nSnapshot; claim; bounded finding set; exact operations; dry-run validation; mutation; post-checks; evidence comment; metric delta; cursor checkpoint; release."
